s are presented for 29\ngalaxies in which stars were resolved. Most show a finger centered around\nJ-K_s=1 mag. In some cases, there is a red tail extending to J-K_s=2.5 mag.\n(Abstract slightly shortened).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2005 20:56:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-29"}
