significantly different in\ntype-1 and type-2 AGN, although the temperatures were slightly higher in type-2\nAGN than in type-1 AGN. For 9 sources (including 1 type-1 AGN and 3 type-2 AGN)\na scattering model provided a better fit of the soft excess emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2005 10:20:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
