ly, and illustrated by a\ncontinuum-subtracted mosaic image of the SNR, Shajn 147. The final catalogue of\nIPHAS point sources will contain photometry on ~80 million objects. (abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2005 15:27:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
